title: Your Perfect Self
itunes:title: Your Perfect Self
description:
Do you know what your perfect life looks like? Do you know what the perfect version of you looks like? Well in this episode, I am going to break both of those down so that you can become the best version of yourself and also have the best life that you possibly can.
